{"tid":767961,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"令你難受.....對唔住","createTime":"2018-08-05T04:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T04:19:44.000Z","uid":167880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa9c022e7bbc8fca3019a352029bc0d0bf231b6","tid":767961,"uid":167880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:08:37.000Z","msg":"「友情」....卻係他人眼中誤以為「愛情」<br />\n緋聞的出現 我叫你當耳邊風<br />\n無諗過...會令你難受<br />\n<br />\n雖然d閒言閒語都係無中生有<br />\n但我明白其出現的原因...大慨因我 撞向了你的牆<br />\n愚笨 令我走近你<br />\n幼稚 令我失去你<br />\n共你再戀都只是餘震<br />\n<br />\n明知名花有主 仍不斷走近你 <br />\n如今四面楚歌 使你難受無比<br />\n願你待我殘忍 讓我痛愛著你<br />\n<br />\n或許我應該多謝閒言閒語 讓我知道你既想法 讓我不用在猜疑你 讓我知難而退......<br />\n<br />\n或許，我是個壞人，讓愛情變得陰暗又卑賤。<br />\n<br />\n唉 也沒有與你共度患難，有着一同共度喜樂哀愁的經歷，或者是我想多了......始終未登對<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fttdVsF5g0E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfttdVsF5g0E&d=OF85xTxwdB8Jrd18ODRdZ7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7cba1222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fttdVsF5g0E</a><br />\n<br />\n真係好想捉個大喇叭出黎打穫勁"},{"pid":"a4441781f7b472a285d5ae4a1e137af397009bbf","tid":767961,"uid":160781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"離去的 如廢墟中得救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3786a43dcb13e6eb55f7ee67e5ce035677208ee","tid":767961,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"呢個世界唔系凈系得你同佢lor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0415064f61293fffbc8970955b06f7bf965ae3e","tid":767961,"uid":167880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4441781f7b472a285d5ae4a1e137af397009bbf","tid":767961,"uid":160781